alexandria (0.6.3) stable; urgency=medium

  * Stable release

    Maintenance release. Adds iPod Notes export. Removes Refresh
    button. Made library loading asynchronous, with feedback, for more
    responsive GUI. Added tooltips to icon view of books. New Amazon
    ECS 4.0 provider to replace the old AWS 3.x provider, as AWS 3.x
    will be deprecated by Amazon on March 31 2008.

  * Many bugs fixed, including these from the RubyForge tracker:
    #14163, #16708, #16619, #16618, #15329, #14592, #18197, #13302

 -- Cathal Mc Ginley <cathal.alexandria@gnostai.org>  Wed, 20 Feb 2008 13:45:00 +0000

alexandria (0.6.2) stable; urgency=low

  * Stable release
    First new stable version in over 2 years. Adds Smart Libraries which
    are filtered views on your libraries. New support for tagging
    books and filtering on tags. New multi-input method for CueCat barcode
    scanners.

  * Many bugs fixed, including these from the RubyForge tracker:
    #2518 #2533 #3130 #5911 #6742 #8173 #8719 #9545 #13482 #11170
    #11306 #14164 #1423 #14592 #15510 #15924 #16355 #16356

 -- Cathal Mc Ginley <cathal.alexandria@gnostai.org>  Thu, 20 Dec 2007 01:30:00 +0000

